OL,3,CCumbrian food bank donations reach a
OL,4,Cnew low
OL,6,FA cumbrian food bank says it may have
OL,7,Fto make "horrible decisions" on who to
OL,8,Fhelp, as donations reach a new low
OL,9,Famid fears of closure.
OL,11,FWindermere & District Food Bank says
OL,12,Ftheir service only has supplies for
OL,13,Fthe next three months, and needs at
OL,14,Fleast six months' supply to stay
OL,15,Fafloat.
OL,17,FThe food bank has supported people who
OL,18,Fneed it for the last 11 years across
OL,19,FWindermere, Ambleside, Kendal and
OL,20,FBowness.
