OL,4,Cnew low
OL,6,FTheir food supplies help 26 households
OL,7,F- or 60 people - on average per week
OL,8,Fwith essential food parcels.
OL,10,FIan Winters, the Team Lead, says a big
OL,11,F"challenge" is the decrease in
OL,12,Ffinancial donations.
OL,14,FHe said: "In the last week alone,
OL,15,Fwe've served 30 families, which is
OL,16,Fprobably a 25% increase on previous
OL,17,Fweeks. So families with four or five
OL,18,Fchildren maybe, right down to single
OL,19,Findividuals.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
