OL,6,F"The main challenge we are facing is
OL,7,Fthat monetary donations are down.
OL,8,FThey've fallen off a cliff really in
OL,9,Fthe last three months or so. And
OL,10,Fthat's put us in, we hope, what is a
OL,11,Ftemporary funding crisis.
OL,13,F"Essentially, we need #2,000 a month
OL,14,Fto keep going. And the reason we need
OL,15,Fmonetary support is to buy in some of
OL,16,Fthe stocks you see. Without that, we
OL,17,Fwouldn't be able to give a balanced
OL,18,Fdiet to our clients every week."
