OL,3,CCumbrian food bank donations reach a
OL,4,Cnew low
OL,6,FThe Windermere food bank says
OL,7,Fdonations are 'simply not' keeping up
OL,8,Fwith the current demand.
OL,10,FCumbrian MP Tim Farron says it is
OL,11,F"heartbreaking" to see more people
OL,12,Fthan ever using food banks.
OL,14,FThe Westmorland and Lonsdale MP Tim
OL,15,FFarron, said: "People who I know up
OL,16,Funtil a few years ago were regular
OL,17,Fgivers to food banks, now they have to
OL,18,Fgo to them themselves.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
