OL,6,F"I can think of individuals I can
OL,7,Fthink of families and it's
OL,8,Fheartbreaking and for them - it feels
OL,9,Fcrushing in terms of their dignity as
OL,10,Fwell."
OL,12,FMr Farron believes building council
OL,13,Fhouses for local families could be a
OL,14,Fsolution, he said: "That would be the
OL,15,Ffirst thing you do. Secondly, we'd be
OL,16,Fmaking sure that public transport
OL,17,Freached everywhere and that it was
OL,18,Faffordable. So the Government must
OL,19,Fkeep that cap on fares.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
