OL,6,F"And then we've got to look at those
OL,7,Fthings which drive poverty, taking
OL,8,Faway the winter fuel allowance from
OL,9,Fpeople who are on what, 11 and a half
OL,10,Fthousand pounds a year, you know,
OL,11,Fbarely half the minimum wage. That's
OL,12,Foutrageous. And that drives older
OL,13,Fpeople into poverty.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
