OL,3,CCumbrian food bank donations reach a
OL,4,Cnew low
OL,6,F"And then the two child benefit cap is
OL,7,Fsomething which punishes children. And
OL,8,Fall the evidence is that it drives
OL,9,Fpoverty. So poverty doesn't happen by
OL,10,Faccident. And whilst we all have
OL,11,Fpersonal responsibility, as a
OL,12,FGovernment and as politicians, we've
OL,13,Fgot a duty to try and make sure we
OL,14,Fminimise it."
OL,16,FThe Government says it is helping
OL,17,Fvulnerable people across the UK with
OL,18,Fthe costs of energy, food and water
OL,19,Fthis winter through its five hundred
OL,20,Fmillion pound Household Support Fund.
