OL,6,FThe Trussell Trust, a national food
OL,7,Fbank charity, believes more than nine
OL,8,Fmillion people will turn to using food
OL,9,Fbanks during the winter - one million
OL,10,Fmore users than five years ago.
OL,12,FMr Winters says the food bank has had
OL,13,Fto start "making qualitative
OL,14,Fdecisions".
