OL,6,FBut there is one family who uses the
OL,7,FWindermere food bank that stays in Mr
OL,8,FWinters' mind, he added: "A local
OL,9,Ffamily where a 17-year old girl has
OL,10,Fbecome the head of the household
OL,11,Flooking after a 15-year old and a two-
OL,12,Fyear old sibling.
OL,14,F"Nobody should be put in that position
OL,15,Fat that age. That's where we can step
OL,16,Fin and support in that situation and
OL,17,Fnot just give emergency food, but give
OL,18,Fthem the ability to hopefully find a
OL,19,Fway out of that crisis."
